data.description: "Discover the epitome of refined living in this Boynton Beach gem. The single-family residence features an airy open-concept design, encompassing 4 bedrooms and 2 full baths. Recent updates within the past 5 years include all major appliances, air conditioning, and the water heater, ensuring a blend of modern convenience and efficiency.    Elegance takes center stage in the tasteful remodel, showcasing crown molding, laminate flooring, and 5-inch baseboards. This residence seamlessly marries timeless sophistication with contemporary comforts. Enjoy the utmost convenience with proximity to shopping plazas and dining options, creating a lifestyle of ease.
